properties.headline: FLOODING WILCANNIA TO IVANHOE Cobb Highway between Barrier Highway and Columbus Street
properties.diversions:
Southbound from Wilcannia: Barrier Hwy to Cobar, Kidman Way to Goolgowi, and Mid Western Hwy to Hay.

Northbound from Hay: Mid Western Hwy to Goolgowi, Kidman Way to Cobar, and Barrier Hwy to Wilcannia.

This route is suitable for all vehicles and will add around 4hrs to your travel time.

properties.headline: FLOODING DUNEDOO Castlereagh Highway near Allweather Road
properties.diversions:
Light vehicles can use Golden Hwy and Mendooran Rd, or Newell Hwy to rejoin the Castlereagh Hwy.

Heavy vehicles can use Golden Hwy and Newell Hwy to rejoin the Castlereagh Hwy.
